The vast majority of Michigan residents are eligible to receive a stimulus check from the federal government this year. Even if you have no income, you are still eligible, but need to take action to receive your stimulus payment. This includes individuals with low or no earnings who normally don't file taxes. Please see the website below to learn how to take action.https://poverty.umich.edu/stimulus-checks/?fbclid=IwAR2gHv_lbB1cSywEhiawOEAEXPEzEccjcRSM9si9NEfNpz6sH4MaR90_4gM&nbsp;

